topic.title: Dogecoin price predictions
topic.body:
This thread dedicated to dogecoin price prediction.

I believe dogecoin will go to one dollar now by 2022 due to everyone sees the power of the collective to drive market prices and activity in general. The people know now the power they have held this whole time previously unknown.

I believe dogecoin will be to ten dollar by 2025 even if people continue to realize the power.

What you all believe?
